{"tid":1267184,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"為慶祝建國70周年　習近平宣布特赦9種罪犯","createTime":"2019-06-29T18:15:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-06T05:13:16.000Z","uid":8441,"like":2,"dislike":72,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"345e9cb24b752ce184933875fb9eddd79412893b","tid":1267184,"uid":8441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T18:15:37.000Z","msg":"國家主席習近平在中華人民共和國成立70周年之際，簽署並發布特赦令，對部分服刑罪犯給予特赦安排。<br />\n<br />\n新華社報道，獲得特赦的9種罪犯，包括曾參與抗日戰爭、或其他保衛國家主權的戰事、年滿75歲、身體有嚴重殘疾等罪犯，但不包括干犯貪污受賄、殺人、強姦等嚴重犯罪。<br />\n<br />\n報道指，根據黨中央部署，特赦部分罪犯，有利弘揚國內全面依法治國理念，展現中國人權司法保障水平，進一步樹立開放、民主、的國際形象。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nsource rthk <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1465756-20190629.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1465756-20190629.htm&d=FGEw0iwwiNltpS2R1LMyGrtp0LkHB2EL0pKzUaHUqTQ%3D&h=63ce5974\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1465756-20190629.htm&h=c3665fb9\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1465756-20190629.htm</a>"},{"pid":"62caa1b5f2545f14aaa493cd6c2ba32363ebca4d","tid":1267184,"uid":243380,"like":41,"dislike":0,"score":41,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T18:16:21.000Z","msg":"有撚形象咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aecc5571e147c7d6fd4bb9aea1d60e09a179af9d","tid":1267184,"uid":153722,"like":53,"dislike":0,"score":53,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T18:18:49.000Z","msg":"75歲趕出去乞食啦<br />\n咪撚晒9我米飯"},{"pid":"17d89b839742f2faf2b35d27cb5e7222d99e316f","tid":1267184,"uid":235152,"like":29,"dislike":0,"score":29,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T18:20:43.000Z","msg":"放左維權律師啦屌"},{"pid":"03093f212643968fb69956f625d66d3d098a0a7c","tid":1267184,"uid":1790,"like":26,"dislike":0,"score":26,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T18:24:04.000Z","msg":"參與抗日戰爭=國民黨人？"},{"pid":"242b1c194097039d60dd7a14c84221a86064ccba","tid":1267184,"uid":103156,"lik